        <mxCell id="22" value="1. User presses Run or Scheduler fires&#xa;2. Cloud Run reads changed MDX from GitHub&#xa;3. Cache check happens in Neon&#xa;4. Changed sections go to RunPod&#xa;5. Results, tokens, latency, quality go back to Neon&#xa;6. Output docs pushed to GitHub&#xa;7. Ops Web + Grafana show the result" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ffffff;strokeColor=#666666;fontSize=14;" vertex="1" parent="1">
